    <h1>CoachCraft Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 14, 2025</p>

    <p>
      CoachCraft is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy
      explains how we handle your information when you use our app.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

    <p>
      When you choose to sign in with Facebook or Google, we receive basic
      profile information from these services, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Profile picture (if available)</li>
      <li>A unique identifier from the service</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This information is used solely to create and maintain your account. We do
      not collect any additional personal information beyond what's necessary
      for authentication and basic account functionality.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

    <p>The information we receive from Facebook and Google is used to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create and maintain your CoachCraft account</li>
      <li>Authenticate you when you sign in</li>
      <li>Display your name and profile picture in the app</li>
      <li>Contact you if necessary regarding your account</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We do not use your information for advertising, marketing, or any other
      purposes beyond basic app functionality.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>

    <p>
      Your authentication information is securely stored on our servers. Any
      training data you create (such as training plans, notes, or settings) is
      associated with your account and stored securely. We implement
      industry-standard security measures to protect your information.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>

    You may access the Personal Information we hold about you and to update
    and/or correct it, subject to certain exceptions. If you wish to access your
    Personal Information, please contact us in writing. CoachCraft will not
    charge any fee for your access request, but may charge an administrative fee
    for providing a copy of your Personal Information. In order to protect your
    Personal Information we may require identification from you before releasing
    the requested information.

    <p>
      To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information below.
    </p>

    <h2>No Tracking</h2>

    <p>
      Beyond the authentication services mentioned above, we do not use cookies,
      analytics, advertising, or any tracking technologies. We do not monitor
      your usage patterns or collect any behavioral data.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Authentication Services</h2>

    <p>
      CoachCraft uses Facebook and Google authentication services to allow you
      to sign in with your existing accounts. When you choose to sign in with
      these services:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Facebook:</strong> Your use of Facebook Login is governed by Facebook's
        Data Policy. We only receive the basic profile information you consent to
        share.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Google:</strong> Your use of Google Sign-In is governed by Google's
        Privacy Policy. We only receive the basic profile information you consent
        to share.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      You can revoke CoachCraft's access to your Facebook or Google account at
      any time through your respective account settings on those platforms.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>

    <p>
      We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third
      parties, except:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>When you explicitly consent to such sharing</li>
      <li>When required by law or to protect our legal rights</li>
      <li>
        With service providers who help us operate the app (who are bound by
        confidentiality agreements)
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

    <p>
      If we ever change how we handle data in the future, we will update this
      privacy policy and notify users of any significant changes. Any changes
      will only apply to future versions of the app.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <p>
      If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:coachcraft.platform@gmail.com"
        >coachcraft.platform@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>
